Just a reminder…. the Covid death rate is 0.2%. I’m not a mathematician but this seems like a simple calculation …. 99,8% will survive! It’s a bloody miracle!🤓But they still want to speed up the process, cut and paste with DNA and avoid regulations that are supposed to PROTECT US… but don’t worry they are doing it so they can SAVE US! I don’t get it…do you?? #icallbullshit ✌️ ⁣ ⁣ ⁣ ⁣ ⁣ ⁣ ⁣
